data.description: SELLER WILL PAY CLOSING COSTS! Welcome to your dream home at 488 Private Road 1507, Bandera, TX! This meticulously maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem is nestled on a spacious .27-acre lot within the gated community of Bandera Estates. Boasting a 2020 Fleetwood Weston G Home, this property exudes modern comfort and relaxation. With an 18' x 35' boathouse on a concrete slab, it's a perfect blend of indoor and outdoor living for those who love to embrace the Texas Hill Country lifestyle. Whether you're looking for a permanent residence or a vacation property, this home at 488 Private Road 1507 offers the best of both worlds. Immerse yourself in the beauty of the Texas Hill Country while enjoying the convenience and amenities of a gated community. Make this charming property your own and experience the warmth of Bandera's close-knit community. Contact us today to schedule a private viewing and start living the Hill Country lifestyle you've always dreamed of.
